{
  "texts": [
    "The data from these tables suggest that in emotion analysis tasks, integrating visual, auditory, and textual information provides richer contextual cues, thereby improving the predictive accuracy and robustness of the model.",
    "This multimodal fusion approach is vitally significant for developing efficient and accurate emotion analysis tools.",
    "It also suggests that researchers designing multimodal emotion analysis models should consider the characteristics and contributions of each modality to better capture and understand human emotional expressions.",
    "To investigate the specific contributions of the TK and LG modules to model performance, this paper presents a detailed analysis of a series of ablation experiments conducted on the MOSEI and MOSI datasets.",
    "These results are presented in tables, comparing key performance metrics of the model under different configurations, including binary classification accuracy, F1 score), mean absolute error, correlation, multi-class accuracy, and the number of model parameters (Param).The results clearly demonstrate that the introduction of the TK and LG modules significantly enhances the model's performance on most metrics."
  ]
}